Package: aima-aibook
Version: 0.4.0+aibook20260510.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: AIMA <support@aimaserver.com>
Installed-Size: 24080
Depends: systemd, xdg-utils
Recommends: curl
Description: AIMA for Moore Threads AIBook
 AIMA local AI inference manager packaged for Moore Threads AIBook devices.
 This package installs the AIMA binary, systemd service, desktop launcher,
 and desktop icon. Models, engine images, Docker, K3S, and cloud identity
 state are intentionally not included.
